text: Hunter Cantwell (born December 30, 1985 in Chattanooga, Tennessee) is a retired American football quarterback who played for on the practice squad for the Carolina Panthers and the Baltimore Ravens of the National Football League (NFL). Cantwell played college football at the University of Louisville. He was undrafted and started his NFL career in 2009 and ended his NFL career in 2011. He is currently the quarterbacks coach for Campbellsville University. ==References== ==Other websites== *Hunter Cantwell at carolinapanthers.com Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Baltimore Ravens players Category:Carolina Panthers players Category:American football quarterbacks Category:Sportspeople from Chattanooga, Tennessee
